5179\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635613\",\"caption_id\":\"137474\",\"seq\":\"30\",\"text\":\"The Computer& the Internet are like fantastic\nassistants for teachers\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"163.319\",\"dur\":\"5.861\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595179\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635614\",\"caption_id\":\"137474\",\"seq\":\"31\",\"text\":\"In other words, modern technologies can complement\ntraditional teaching & learning methods,\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"169.18\",\"dur\":\"5.82\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595179\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635615\",\"caption_id\":\"137474\",\"seq\":\"32\",\"text\":\"not be a replacement for these traditions.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"176\",\"dur\":\"2\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595179\",\"updated_at\":null}]'),(2,'68017','TKhnnmGnLhc.jpg','IELTS - TECHNOLOGY RUINS YOUR LOVE',NULL,'[{\"id\":\"29635978\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"1\",\"text\":\"Hello. Welcome to IELTS KILLER\nThe video series which gives you the best\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"10.37\",\"dur\":\"4.519\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635979\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"2\",\"text\":\"ideas to use in your important IELTS Writing\nEssay\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"14.889\",\"dur\":\"3.241\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635980\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"3\",\"text\":\"Letu2019s look at todayu2019s topic\nThe development of technology changes the\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"18.13\",\"dur\":\"5.6\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635981\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"4\",\"text\":\"way people connect with each other.\nIn which way the development of technology\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"23.73\",\"dur\":\"5.469\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635982\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"5\",\"text\":\"change the types of relationships that people\nmake?\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"29.199\",\"dur\":\"3.2\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635983\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"6\",\"text\":\"It has positive or negative effects on the\nrelationships?\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"32.399\",\"dur\":\"5.391\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635984\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"7\",\"text\":\"notice the keywords here\nin which way u2013 change u2013 relationships\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"37.79\",\"dur\":\"5.97\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635985\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"8\",\"text\":\"u2013 positive u2013 negative\nIn this essay, you have to analyze how technology\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"43.76\",\"dur\":\"7.459\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635986\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"9\",\"text\":\"has changed our relationships\n& that change is good or bad.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"51.219\",\"dur\":\"4.951\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635987\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"10\",\"text\":\"Well, itu2019s clear that technology has revolutionized\nthe concept of communication\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"57.1\",\"dur\":\"6.09\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635988\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"11\",\"text\":\"& led to a considerable change in the relationships\nwe have\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"63.19\",\"dur\":\"4.27\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635989\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"12\",\"text\":\"Of course, there are beneficial changes as\nwell as detrimental ones.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"67.46\",\"dur\":\"6.92\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635990\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"13\",\"text\":\"The most significant impact of technology\non communication\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"74.38\",\"dur\":\"4.44\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635991\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"14\",\"text\":\"is that the speed has incredibly risen\n& the cost has been drastically cut.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"78.82\",\"dur\":\"6.51\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635992\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"15\",\"text\":\"The computer & internet have made the process\nof creating & editing documents easy\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"85.33\",\"dur\":\"6.13\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635993\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"16\",\"text\":\"Besides, amazing features such as spell check\n& grammar check can be applied automatically.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"91.46\",\"dur\":\"7.199\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635994\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"17\",\"text\":\"Moreover, distance is no longer a barrier\nas email allows sending a document to any\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"98.659\",\"dur\":\"7.42\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635995\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"18\",\"text\":\"part of the world within seconds\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"106.079\",\"dur\":\"3.65\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635996\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"19\",\"text\":\"Thanks to modern communication technology,\npeople now enjoy lots of convenience & efficiency.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"109.729\",\"dur\":\"6.39\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635997\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"20\",\"text\":\"Firstly, relationships have become better\nb/c people are connected to each other all\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"117.1\",\"dur\":\"5.68\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635998\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"21\",\"text\":\"the time\n& there is little chance of misunderstanding\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"122.78\",\"dur\":\"3.83\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29635999\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"22\",\"text\":\"due to communication gap.\nSecondly, the Internet helps spread our network\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"126.61\",\"dur\":\"5.87\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29636000\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"23\",\"text\":\"by tracking down old friends and teachers\nWell, if you use Facebook & Twitter, you know\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"132.48\",\"dur\":\"5.89\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29636001\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"24\",\"text\":\"how to do this\nFinally, it creates new business opportunities\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"138.37\",\"dur\":\"5.589\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29636002\",\"caption_id\":\"137475\",\"seq\":\"25\",\"text\":\"by assisting business owners in seeking potential\ncustomers & business partners.\",\"translate_comment\":null,\"start\":\"143.959\",\"dur\":\"5.211\",\"is_scores\":null,\"created_at\":\"1532595521\",\"updated_at\":null},{\"id\":\"29636003\",